{"id":113311,"date":"2020-07-28T13:59:03","date_gmt":"2020-07-28T13:59:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/?p=109267"},"modified":"2020-07-28T13:59:03","modified_gmt":"2020-07-28T13:59:03","slug":"financial-commission-announces-execution-quality-certification-of-samtrade-fx","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/2020\/07\/28\/financial-commission-announces-execution-quality-certification-of-samtrade-fx\/","title":{"rendered":"Financial Commission Announces Execution Quality Certification of Samtrade FX","gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"text"}]},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">July 28, 2020, The Financial Commission today announces execution certification for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.samtradefx.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Samtrade FX<\/a>, an approved member of the Commission using Verify My Trade, a \u201cvalue-added\u201d service launched several years ago to promote pricing and execution transparency in the Forex market.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Verified order execution quality<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Following the launch of order execution verification with Verify My Trade (VMT) in September of 2018, Financial Commission broker members continue to apply for certification of their order execution quality as a step to increase transparency regarding execution speed and pricing.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Today, Samtrade FX becomes the latest Financial Commission member to have successfully completed the VMT certification, having satisfied all execution quality standards set out for all members of the Commission. Trades can now view the execution audit results for Samtrade FX directly on our website, by <a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/samtrade-fx\/\">clicking here<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Check your broker\u2019s status<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">All interested parties can now view the execution audit results for members of the Financial Commission using VMT certifications by visiting our\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/members\/participating-members-of-the-financial-commission\/\">Members page<\/a>\u00a0or the profile pages of brokers listed in our Members section. Certified brokers will be highlighted with a unique badge as displayed below.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.verifymytrade.com\/badge\/d535b3cf-cae4-4f59-bfd7-7d11eb86b316?lang=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"lazyautosizes lazyloaded aligncenter wp-image-98359 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-300x280.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-200x187.png 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-300x280.png 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-400x374.png 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-600x561.png 600w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-768x718.png 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-800x748.png 800w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-1024x957.png 1024w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-1200x1121.png 1200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2.png 1787w\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"280\" data-src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-300x280.png\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-200x187.png 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-300x280.png 300w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-400x374.png 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-600x561.png 600w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-768x718.png 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-800x748.png 800w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-1024x957.png 1024w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2-1200x1121.png 1200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.com.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/\u0432\u043c\u0442-\u0449\u0438\u0442-2.png 1787w\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-orig-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">By clicking on the badge users will navigate to a dedicated webpage for each broker that will indicate the last time an audit was performed, how many orders were analyzed, and whether the results satisfied the order execution standards established by VMT.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">If you are interested in using the VMT service or would like more information, please reach out to us at\u00a0<a href=\"mailto:info@financialcommission.com.co\">info@financialcommission.com.co<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>About the Financial Commission<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Founded in 2013, the Financial Commission is a leading independent member-driven external dispute resolution (EDR) organization for international online brokerages, exchanges, and Blockchain firms that participate in global foreign exchange (forex), derivatives, CFD and digital asset markets.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Financial Commission provides efficient compliance solutions to its members, alongside its External Dispute Resolution (EDR) mechanism that serves as an effective channel for processing complaints from clients of member firms.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For more information please contact us at\u00a0<a href=\"mailto:info@financialcommission.com.co\">info@financialcommission.com.co<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>July 28, 2020, The Financial Commission today announces execution certification for Samtrade FX, an approved member of the Commission using Verify My Trade, a \u201cvalue-added\u201d service launched several years ago to promote pricing and execution transparency in the Forex market. Verified order execution quality Following the launch of order execution verification with Verify My Trade [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"author":2,"featured_media":103089,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[14,12,6817,15,16],"tags":[55,56,57,58,59,60,61,62,63,64,65,66,67,68,69,70,71,72,73,74,75],"class_list":["post-113311","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-commission-news","category-company-news-news-events","category-fexp","category-press-release","category-press-releas